source: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTRESIDENCE_00783_Q2_000_120<tab>In order to renovate the cozy cabin, you must continue to develop your island and increase your sanctuary rank.
target: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTRESIDENCE_00783_Q2_000_120<tab>Du kannst deine Strandhütte weiter ausbauen, sobald du mehr Land erschlossen und eine höhere Inselstufe erreicht hast.

source: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTRESIDENCE_00783_Q2_000_200<tab>This appears to be a log with a board attached to it. How quaint.
target: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTRESIDENCE_00783_Q2_000_200<tab>Dies scheint die Leittafel für die Strandhütte zu sein.
